Holy, Holy Holy   圣哉，圣哉，圣哉
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0koY7Lhe9EE

Holy, holy, holy
Lord, God Almighty
Early in the morning, our song shall rise to Thee

Holy, holy, holy
Merciful and mighty
God in three persons blessed Trinity

Holy, holy, holy
Though the darkness hides Thee
Though the eye of sinful man thy glory may not see
Only Thou art holy; there is none beside Thee
Perfect in power, in love, and purity

Holy, holy, holy
Lord, God Almighty
All Thy works shall praise Thy name in earth and sky and sea
Holy, holy, holy
Merciful and mighty
God in three persons blessed Trinity

⸻

Interlaced Hanzi ↔ Pinyin

圣哉，圣哉，圣哉，全能大主宰！
Shèng zāi, shèng zāi, shèng zāi, quánnéng dà zhǔzǎi!

清晨我众歌颂，欢声上达天庭；
Qīngchén wǒ zhòng gēsòng, huānshēng shàng dá tiāntíng;

圣哉，圣哉，圣哉，慈悲全能主宰，
Shèng zāi, shèng zāi, shèng zāi, cíbēi quánnéng zhǔzǎi,

赞美三一神，父子与圣灵。
Zànměi Sānyī Shén, Fùzǐ yǔ Shènglíng.

⸻

圣哉，圣哉，圣哉，众圣都敬拜，
Shèng zāi, shèng zāi, shèng zāi, zhòng shèng dōu jìngbài,

放下黄金冠冕，环绕在水晶海；
Fàngxià huángjīn guānmiǎn, huánrào zài shuǐjīng hǎi;

千万天使天军，俯伏叩拜主前，
Qiānwàn tiānshǐ tiānjūn, fǔfú kòubài zhǔ qián,

昔在而今在，永在亿万年。
Xī zài ér jīn zài, yǒng zài yì wàn nián.

⸻

圣哉，圣哉，圣哉，主庄严威荣；
Shèng zāi, shèng zāi, shèng zāi, zhǔ zhuāngyán wēiróng;

罪人昏昧难见，因黑暗罪深重；
Zuìrén hūnmèi nán jiàn, yīn hēi’àn zuì shēnzhòng;

惟独上主至圣，惟独上主至尊，
Wéidú Shàngzhǔ zhìshèng, wéidú Shàngzhǔ zhìzūn,

全能又全爱，至圣洁真神。
Quánnéng yòu quán’ài, zhì shèngjié zhēnshén.

⸻

圣哉，圣哉，圣哉，全能大主宰！
Shèng zāi, shèng zāi, shèng zāi, quánnéng dà zhǔzǎi!

地上天空海洋，万物同颂主名；
Dìshàng tiānkōng hǎiyáng, wànwù tóng sòng zhǔ míng;

圣哉，圣哉，圣哉，慈悲全能主宰，
Shèng zāi, shèng zāi, shèng zāi, cíbēi quánnéng zhǔzǎi,

赞美三一神，父子与圣灵。
Zànměi Sānyī Shén, Fùzǐ yǔ Shènglíng.


